Who is BARD Games?
It has been a while! A lot has happened since A Band of Orcs descended on your game table; Stranger Things made gamer kids cool, politics took over the news and I started a board game publishing company with my good friend Eric!
BARD Games is dedicated to games we believe in. On our website, we feature our game projects and other games (in print) that we love. Check us out here;
